name: FACE HACK Precision Sculpting Cream Contour Bronzer Stick
about: What it is: A cream bronzer stick that contours, sculpts, and creates dimension in a blendable, blurring plant-derived formula...Coverage: Light..Finish: Natural..Formulation: Stick..Highlighted Ingredients:.- Plant Squalane: Provides skin barrier protection..- Moringa Oil: Acts as a moisturizing antioxidant..- Shea Butter: Hydrates...Ingredient Callouts: This product is vegan, gluten-free, and cruelty-free...What Else You Need to Know: This multipurpose bronzer stick is the ultimate face hack. The almond shape applicator contours, sculpts, and creates dimension. The natural-finish, blendable, and blurring formula melts seamlessly into skin for immediate payoff...
ingredients: -Plant Squalane: Provides skin barrier protection..-Moringa Oil: Acts as a moisturizing antioxidant..-Shea Butter: Hydrates. ..Dimethicone, Diisostearyl Malate, Hydrogenated Polydecene, Silica, Vinyl Dimethicone/Methicone Silsesquioxane Crosspolymer, Neopentyl Glycol Dicaprate, Diethylhexyl Carbonate, Synthetic Wax, Polyethylene, Dimethicone/Vinyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Polysilicone-11, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Bis-Diglyceryl Polyacyladipate-2, Sorbitan Isostearate, Squalane, Nymphaea Odorata Root Extract, Nelumbo Nucifera Flower Extract, Gardenia Florida Fruit Extract, Tocopherol, Moringa Oil/Hydrogenated Moringa Oil Esters, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Isopropyl Myristate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Lecithin, Isostearic Acid, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Aluminum Oxide, CI 77491/ CI 77492/ CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), CI 19140 (Yellow 5 Lake)...The list of ingredients is subject to change, please consult the packaging of the product purchased.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:.-Glide over foundation or bare skin to the high points of the face to add warmth, or to forehead, cheekbones, and jawline to create depth and dimension. .-Use the unique almond shape applicator to sculpt and refine as desired.
